{"tid":1296882,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日疑似有人冒警查我身份證","createTime":"2019-07-08T13:28:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T16:09:11.000Z","uid":243691,"like":89,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"041b12963daa5c2e04b0150fd0522559573362e5","tid":1296882,"uid":243691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:28:39.000Z","msg":"行行下路突然有個著黑色背心既人行過黎查我身份證<br />\n我問佢點解佢唔係著藍色制服<br />\n佢話佢係便衣 <br />\n咁我就問佢你有冇委任證<br />\n佢話警察做野唔洗出示委任證<br />\n我見佢條腰有腰帶又有掛住水樽同碌棍<br />\n又有個對講機<br />\n但係冇警員編號<br />\n係哩個情況下 我點知佢係咪冒警想偷我資料？<br />\n<br />\n利申：支持香港警察 支持嚴正執法 愛國愛黨 有出席撐警大會 撐修例"},{"pid":"9efedc1bb371e8889c8d2bba6d273bd92aad83b0","tid":1296882,"uid":243691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:28:53.000Z","msg":"撐警察 撐香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae2961d094e30087c5ebce3ed9560cfcbb70b75c","tid":1296882,"uid":243691,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:30:07.000Z","msg":"好驚 會唔會有犯罪集團襯哩個機會竊取市民資料？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e27fdc2f2cbe6135273b42972ff0b31adad412b5","tid":1296882,"uid":48,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:30:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gojkGS2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgojkGS2.png&h=a971363b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba9afb7aba689aedf962543df86cceeeb8391823","tid":1296882,"uid":243691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e27fdc2f2cbe6135273b42972ff0b31adad412b5","tid":1296882,"uid":48,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:30:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gojkGS2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgojkGS2.png&h=a971363b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:30:55.000Z","msg":"佢地兩個都有編號bo"},{"pid":"517876ad4e31c